The Board of Directors of Fidelity Bank Plc in a statement tagged “Rebuttal Of False Information” endorsed by Ejike Ndiulo Brand and Communications of the Bank and sent to The AmehNews saying Our attention has been drawn to false information posted on some online platforms alleging that management of the bank has approved a probe of our former Managing Director/CEO, Mr. Nnamdi Okonkwo The story is entirely false, malicious and should be discountenanced Mr.  Okonkwo served the bank meritoriously as Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer between 2014 and 2020 and led his team to achieve impressive results. For the avoidance of doubt, the Board of Directors continues to hold Mr. Okonkwo in high esteem and wish him well in his future endeavors.